Package edu.ncsu.csc216.issue_manager.model.issue

Class Issue

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.issue_manager.model.issue.Issue
  • public class Issue
extends java.lang.Object
    Issue class which has the IssueState, NewState, WorkingState, VerifyingState, ConfirmedState, and ClosedState inner classes Acts as a ticketing system for enhancements or bugs for developers to adjust and testers to comment on
    Author:
    yash
